| **Labels** | `app: survey` matches everywhere. | Pods become "orphans." |
| **Image** | `hansyy/survey-app:v6` exists. | `ErrImagePull` |
| **Ports** | `containerPort: 8080`. | 404/Connection Refused. |
| **Context** | Are you in the `dev` namespace? | Deploying to the wrong environment. |

